                <note rend="inline" type="source">Paris Peace Conference 184.02202/8:
                    Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                        to the Consul at Helsingfors</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Haynes</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-03-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 22, 1919</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3. Inform Pettit that he should withdraw from Russia immediately and return to
                    Paris as soon as possible. It is not desired to maintain communication office in
                    Russia or courier service between Helsingfors and Petrograd at present.</p>
                <closer>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Am</hi>[<hi rend="smallcaps">erican</hi>] <hi
                        rend="smallcaps">Mission</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
